    "Full text references are always included.",
    "This increases the reliability of the answers and reduces the level of hallucination.",
    "Hallucinations sometimes occur in the LLM when the model produces false or invented information that still sounds convincing.",
    "This can make it difficult to fully trust the model's answers, even when full text references are provided.",
    "We will come back to how to deal with these issues-and how to improve trust in the results generated-in Section 7."
